Cooggerup is site where you can get basic account information on your steemit account. It has an upvote bot in discord channel.

Features Of Coogerup

Cooggerup can show you basic account infoormation

It can show you list of followers 

It can show steemit users who you are following but not following you

It can show the vote wrth of people that voted yoour post on steemit 

It shows the value of coins in $

It shows the information in a post 

It shows pending payout information on a post 

It can tell you the ammount of btc you will get if you try to convert from steem

It shows the value of steem, sbd, btc and ltc. 

More features coming soon 
